      "amount": "1 tablespoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "vanilla extract",
      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "chopped walnuts",
      "amount": "1/2 cup"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Combine flour, baking powder, and salt in a bowl.",
    "In another bowl whisk oat milk, eggs, miso, maple syrup, and vanilla until smooth.",
    "Pour wet mixture into dry and stir until just combined; do not overmix.",
    "Fold in chopped walnuts gently.",
    "Heat a nonstick skillet over medium heat and lightly oil with coconut oil spray.",
    "Pour 1/4 cup batter per pancake onto skillet, cooking until bubbles form on surface.",
    "Flip pancakes and cook until golden brown, about 2 minutes each side.",
    "Serve hot drizzled with extra maple syrup and a sprinkle of walnuts.",
    "Enjoy a sweet and savory brunch treat."
